Package: wbcmd
Title: Wrapper Functions for 'Connectome Workbench' Commands
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel", , "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
Description: Provides R wrapper functions for the 'Connectome Workbench'
    command-line tool ('wb_command'). Includes a central dispatcher for
    executing workbench commands, environment detection, and convenience
    wrappers for common operations on CIFTI, GIFTI, and surface files.
